  <brief_title>UEMR for Medium-sized Pedunculated Colon Polyps</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Use of Underwater Endoscopic Mucosal Resection for Medium-sized Pedunculated Colon Polyps: A Prospective Observational Study</official_title>
