  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Underwater EMR (UEMR) is an emerging technique for endoscopic resection. The purpose of this&#xD;
      research is to observ wether the UEMR for medium-sized pedunculated polyps is safe and&#xD;
      effective.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <overall_status>Not yet recruiting</overall_status>
